No. 821,

Mise.

Sibron v. New York. Gretchen White Ober-man and Leon B. Polsky for appellant. Aaron E. Koota for appellee.

Appeal from Ct. App. N. Y. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Probable jurisdiction noted and case transferred to appellate docket.

18 N. Y. 2d 603, 219 N. E. 2d 196.
